kitchens.title: Estancia del Norte San Antonio, Tapestry Collection by Hilton
kitchens.description: Warm quarters, some with balconies, in relaxed hotel featuring a restaurant & an outdoor pool.
kitchens.address: 37 NE Loop 410 At McCullough, San Antonio, TX 78216, United States
kitchens.hotelDescription:
Featuring an old-world vibe, this relaxed hotel is a 5-minute walk from North Star Mall, 2 miles from San Antonio International Airport and 9 miles from The Alamo.
 Warm rooms have Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs and minifridges, as well as tea and coffeemakers. Upgraded rooms add balconies and/or pull-out sofas. Suites provide separate living rooms.
 Amenities include a restaurant, a bar and an outdoor pool, plus a gym. An airport shuttle and breakfast are available, as is parking.
